parameters.name: DefaultVersionNumber
parameters.description: The default version number of the instance launch template.

parameters.name: LaunchTemplateId
parameters.description: The ID of the launch template. You must specify the LaunchTemplateId or LaunchTemplateName parameter to determine an instance launch template.

parameters.name: LaunchTemplateName
parameters.description: The name of the instance launch template. You must specify the LaunchTemplateId or LaunchTemplateName parameter to determine an instance launch template.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The region ID of the launch template. You can call the [DescribeRegions](~~25609~~) operation to query the most recent region list.
